          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Indulge your skin in the antioxidant-rich care of our goji berry beauty soap. Each bar is handcrafted to gently cleanse, hydrate, and restore your skin’s natural glow. Infused with botanical oils and goji berry extract, it’s a daily skincare essential you’ll love using. Our gluta berry soap is customer favorite for brightening and smoothing the skin. Elevate your routine with gentle, nourishing ingredients that make a difference from the first use. Treat your skin to something truly special.</p>"
